<title>USA: Zale has $225 mln working capital facility.</title>
<headline>Zale has $225 mln working capital facility.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Zale Corp said it has entered into a three-year unsecured $225 million working capital facility with a group of nine banks led by BankBoston.</p>
<p>This new agreement replaces an existing $150 million secured bank facility.  It also offers provisions for an extension to a fourth year.</p>
